# Akash Kumar Portfolio

## Stack
Next.js 15 App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, Framer Motion, shadcn/ui, Zod.

## Architecture
- `app/` — routes and pages
- `components/` — UI (`ui/`), layout, sections, cards, motion, shared
- `config/` — site config and navigation
- `data/` — profile, projects, experience, skills (content layer)
- `types/` — shared TypeScript types
- `lib/` — utilities

## Conventions
- Dark theme only (`defaultTheme="dark"`, no system toggle)
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Reuse `Container`, `SectionHeading`, `FadeIn`, `StaggerContainer`
- Content changes go in `data/` and `config/site.ts`, not hardcoded in components
- Static generation for portfolio and project pages
- Accessibility: semantic HTML, labels, skip link, `aria-current`, reduced-motion support
- SEO: metadata, canonical URLs, sitemap, robots, Schema.org JSON-LD, OG images

